title: Opendoor (OPEN) Up or Down on October 23?
description:

This market will resolve to "Down" if the official NASDAQ closing price for Opendoor Technologies Inc. (OPEN) on Thursday, October 23, 2025 is lower than the official NASDAQ closing price for OPEN on the most recent prior trading day.

E.g., ordinarily, a market on Monday would refer to the previous Friday for its most recent closing price, unless that Friday were a market holiday, in which case it would refer to Thursday, or the next most recent trading day.
